| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4964 — Recovery Inhibition (interlock)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: cbcb00e2-dcbc-5e0d-a04b-d5cd7713b3e9"
